Class QueryParser

java.lang.Object
  context.arch.enactor.QueryParser

public class QueryParser
extends java.lang.Object

Parses a bracket-based grammar used in XML files to describe queries. TODO: should use JavaCC or similar parsers to support more intuitive grammars.
